Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
in my opinion, i think it is a good thing. because in the first year, it is necessary for the students to live together to get familiar with the public life, learn how to get on well with the roommates is also an important lesson, from which the students could learn a lot of things.